---

<section id="formularioUnirse" class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-[#5E0B15] text-white overflow-hidden relative">
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/3 h-full opacity-10 hidden md:block">
    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[300px] lg:text-[400px] -mr-32 -mt-16" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">
      account_balance
    </span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 text-center relative z-10">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-headline font-bold mb-6 md:mb-8">
      Forma parte del círculo DETRA
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl font-body text-[#ffb2b7] mb-8 md:mb-12 leading-relaxed">
      Si eres estudiante universitario y tienes vocación investigativa, déjanos tu correo electrónico para enviarte toda la información sobre nuestros próximos procesos de convocatoria y admisión.
    </p>
    <form class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <input
        class="flex-grow bg-white/10 border border-white/20 rounded-lg px-4 md:px-6 py-3 md:py-4 text-white placeholder:text-white/40 focus:bg-white/20 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#ffdadb] transition-all font-body"
        placeholder="Tu correo electrónico"
        type="email"
      />
      <button
        type="submit"
        class="cursor-pointer bg-[#ffdadb] text-[#40000e] px-8 md:px-10 py-3 md:py-4 rounded-lg font-label font-bold text-base md:text-lg hover:bg-white transition-all"
      >
        Enviar
      </button>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>
